{"tid":913089,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一往情深】不忍癡呆妻送護老院受苦 八旬老翁棒殺愛妻","createTime":"2018-11-23T06:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T10:14:10.000Z","uid":130626,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"09be955c2af71e97e18b22e2efd025ee7c4e12cc","tid":913089,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:59:17.000Z","msg":"英國一名八旬老翁不忍把結婚62載、患上認知障礙症的妻子送往老人院，用鐵枝把她打死，被控謀殺。法官判案時形容這是一宗令人悲傷的案件，認為被告對妻子一往情深，輕判他入獄兩年，緩刑兩年。<br />\n84歲老翁弗蘭克斯(Lawrence Franks)與86歲妻子帕特里夏(Patricia Franks)結婚62年。帕特里夏10年前確診患上認知障礙症，她曾懇求丈夫不要送她到護老院，但帕特里夏的病情日漸惡化，不但認不出弗蘭克斯，而且已無法活動兼大小便失禁。雪上加霜的是，弗蘭克斯發覺自已也開始無法自我照顧，加上經常扶帕特里夏上落床和輪椅，令他患上疝氣。<br />\n面對必需把妻子送進護老院的現實，弗蘭克斯今年7月拿起一支搭棚用的鐵枝，猛打愛妻的後腦，還擔心她仍有氣息，再用枕頭把她悶死，之後報警以及致電家人告知一切。警方到場時，帕特里夏證實死亡。弗蘭克斯原被控謀殺，但法官接納他承認誤殺罪，輕判他緩刑，令他不用坐牢。<br />\n法官判案時說，弗蘭克斯對妻子一往情深，不離不棄，一直照顧她，直至自己無法應付，最後唯有遵照妻子的遺願。他形容弗蘭克斯「直至目前，完全是一個好人」。<br />\n帕特里夏的姨甥表示她的家人對弗蘭克斯並無怨恨，「只希望他當初尋求專業人士幫助」。他表示家人相信弗蘭克斯這樣做，完全因為不忍妻子受苦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181123/large/1542944203_46ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181123%2Flarge%2F1542944203_46ad.jpg&h=83d94cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181123/58947193\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F58947193&d=9VGb%2F0e%2BiPoaNMotUy%2Btq%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=47e9253e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F58947193&h=763a1118\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181123/58947193</a>"},{"pid":"589cd26e6c63cf40d633cf4f08cd4033373e5d35","tid":913089,"uid":105738,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:01:41.000Z","msg":"好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但可唔可以殺得痛快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇字都feel到痛"},{"pid":"ba3fe66f5a0a30899ed3184931f691f4aef6a835","tid":913089,"uid":154872,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:06:20.000Z","msg":"有安樂死就唔洗有咁多倫常慘劇案了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f533cfd68c8cc59fb60f79d02e5f84768fde5b1","tid":913089,"uid":216545,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:41:05.000Z","msg":"餵佢食安眠藥再直接用枕頭焗咪算，點解要打頭，爆哂缸好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f676856dc3683fdc7848cd91eb194b873353a22","tid":913089,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:43:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53cc5f59c1c419f2f0d62f51dff32dac3bdf9ac3","tid":913089,"uid":137732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇字都傷心"},{"pid":"5b9dd62a08bf296b7c06a16a8e7d6e499ab37eb0","tid":913089,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n悲劇<br />\n冇人想咁"},{"pid":"dc1c45bf8703d32a0b8ec0018ab12fae25a8276b","tid":913089,"uid":31788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:48:19.000Z","msg":"親手了段一生最愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549a5b84a6a733f58e33e16866aea6088c9e415b","tid":913089,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:52:09.000Z","msg":"論安樂死嘅重要性"},{"pid":"b9505bedaf137b24487458f370eee4a8485dd0e5","tid":913089,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:04:48.000Z","msg":"個男仲慘過死 真係會痛苦到死"},{"pid":"a332d5b8f98932b5e65cd142c56c7ae24ec61f3d","tid"